 594:src/setup.c   ****   /* Clear MOE immediately after enabling timers — matches reference firmware lines 568-569.
 595:src/setup.c   ****    * With OSSR=ENABLE and OSSI=ENABLE, MOE=0 drives:
 596:src/setup.c   ****    *   HIGH-SIDE (HIN) → LOW  via OCIdleState=RESET   (high-side FETs off)
 597:src/setup.c   ****    *   LOW-SIDE  (LIN) → HIGH via OCNIdleState=SET     (low-side FETs on = short-brake)
 598:src/setup.c   ****    * Pins remain in AF_PP mode — BLDC ISR manages MOE going forward.
 599:src/setup.c   ****    * At zero speed: back-EMF=0 → zero braking torque → wheel turns freely. */
